captiveNum 
Behavior: global 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Checks whether the unit is a captive. If the unit is a vehicle, its commander 
 is checked instead. 
If a unit's captivity level was set as a Boolean, then the returned 
 number is either 0 (for false) or 1 (for true). 
Syntax:  
 captiveNum unit 
Parameters: 
unit: Object 
Return Value: 
 Number